conclusion: Solid budget pick under 50€ with flexible I/O but clear weaknesses at 100W sustained (runs too hot). Great for 65W or dual phone/tablet charging thanks to excellent PPS range.
notes: Retractable cable hides fully. Display shows percent, wattage, cycles, temps. Aluminum housing.
